<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="punishment-n">punishment <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'pʌnɪʃmənt/    美 /'pʌnɪʃmənt/  </p>
<p>[U] &amp; [C]</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>惩罚；处罚；刑罚：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Mum says I had better pass my exams, or she will sell the computer <strong>as (a) punishment</strong>.
妈妈说我最好通过考试，否则她会把电脑卖掉以示惩罚。</p><footer>译林⑤ – 1</footer></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>escape punishment
逃避惩罚</p></div></div>